      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 2,
      "text": "The official telc Deutsch A2 Schreiben subtest is completed inside the shared 50-minute Lesen und Schreiben block. It has two tasks: one structured form task and one short personal letter task."
    },
    {
      "id": "n4",
      "type": "heading",
